                      "ep_id": 51,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiao_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "魈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器在白值高的同時，還能提供不錯的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，比較適合魈這種依賴元素爆發輸出的角色。而武器技能提供的暴擊率雖少但對魈比較重要，如果沒有其他五星長槍，該武器對魈來說是比較合適的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 49,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Raiden Shogun_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "雷電將軍",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器能提高基礎攻擊力、",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "和暴擊率，對於主要以元素爆發輸出為主的雷電將軍是個不錯的選擇，同時武器還能提升攻擊速度，提升開大時的輸出能力。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 29,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Shenhe_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "申鶴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "較高的基礎攻擊力能提高申鶴攻擊加成屬性的收益。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "副屬性也能緩解充能壓力，比較適合申鶴使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 50,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiangling_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "香菱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "香菱是一位脫手能力極強的長槍角色，但她開啟元素爆發所需要的能量高達80點，而作為脫手角色，幾乎不能在前臺吃到能量微粒/晶球，該武器不僅白值高且副詞綴提供",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，是十分適合副C香菱的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yun Jin_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "雲堇",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "能給雲堇提供",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
